Titolo: Tom Clancy's EndWar

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Tom Clancy's EndWar  is a strategy video game available on Microsoft Windows and all seventh-generation platforms except the Wii, with the timing and flow of gameplay differing across platforms.  The console and PC version is a real-time tactics game designed by Ubisoft Shanghai, while the handheld versions feature turn-based tactics. It was released on Nintendo DS, PlayStation 3, PlayStation Portable, and Xbox 360 on November 4, 2008, in the United States, November 6, 2008, in Canada, and November 8, 2008, in Europe. A Windows version was released on February 24, 2009. A PlayStation 2 version was cancelled.A sequel was in the works, but due to the game's commercial failure, it was officially cancelled on February 8, 2010.